{"tid":2068370,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高等法院樓梯被塗「法治已死 紅官吳重儀 郭偉健 DLLM」警列刑毁案調查","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T18:46:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":462,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"78ae0f0e704fa29a43b364f6180063baf102fedb","tid":2068370,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200617/photo/bkn-20200617220619901-0617_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200617223952\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200617%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200617220619901-0617_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200617223952&h=5891e623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方於昨日(16日)早上8時許，接獲高等法院保安報警，指低座的樓梯被人塗污。警方到場調查後，將案列作刑事毀壞案，由中區刑事調查隊跟進。根據警方提供的圖片所見，樓梯上被人用黑漆寫上「法治已死」、「紅官」、以及裁判官吳重儀和區域法院法官郭偉健的名字。今晚塗污已被清理。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責此等行為，塗污內容涉及司法機構人員，另外亦帶有辱罵成分，這不僅是違法行為，更會嚴重損害法院的權威及打擊公眾對司法制度的信心。法治是香港的核心價值，警方絕不容許任何人以任何違法方式挑戰法治。警方重申，任何人無合法辯解而摧毀或損壞屬於他人的財產，最高可判處監禁10年。"},{"pid":"d6e3538c7b14c30fbbc391d8bca1d3d17b858f54","tid":2068370,"uid":251732,"like":42,"dislike":20,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a19951571128b0f8734e87fee1f8756538840a","tid":2068370,"uid":58841,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"手足好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6ff8b18c7a58919554811ad17d64c5f816de9b","tid":2068370,"uid":254788,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:01.000Z","msg":"講事實都唔得呀？？<br />\n有冇咁撚惡呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a57df39a112428fbf2d3246509be53995a5b155","tid":2068370,"uid":307619,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"2c09b105707dbf5b5244ee6c23bdc0a4c4ea5c4f","tid":2068370,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"高可晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0ee33db3a9c7276c1dd6c19673fc9c439d11c1","tid":2068370,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"好波！"},{"pid":"17bc539f717eb76cc812425bb170a9f5286e617c","tid":2068370,"uid