ike":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"d6e3538c7b14c30fbbc391d8bca1d3d17b858f54","tid":2068370,"uid":251732,"like":42,"dislike":20,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:42:36.000Z","msg":"下，有咩好割"},{"pid":"e45c898611250dfbfaa42b0b6a6b5d4065fa2ac2","tid":2068370,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:45:21.000Z","msg":"法治是香港的核心價值，警方絕不容許任何人以任何違法方式挑戰法治。<br />\n<br />\n咪你哋破壞得最多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbfc8dbc5302786d4522656a03d6e593a235c2b","tid":2068370,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78ae0f0e704fa29a43b364f6180063baf102fedb","tid":2068370,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200617/photo/bkn-20200617220619901-0617_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200617223952\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200617%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200617220619901-0617_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200617223952&h=5891e623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方於昨日(16日)早上8時許，接獲高等法院保安報警，指低座的樓梯被人塗污。警方到場調查後，將案列作刑事毀壞案，由中區刑事調查隊跟進。根據警方提供的圖片所見，樓梯上被人用黑漆寫上「法治已死」、「紅官」、以及裁判官吳重儀和區域法院法官郭偉健的名字。今晚塗污已被清理。<br />\n<br />\n警方嚴厲譴責此等行為，塗污內容涉及司法機構人員，另外亦帶有辱罵成分，這不僅是違法行為，更會嚴重損害法院的權威及打擊公眾對司法制度的信心。法治是香港的核心價值，警方絕不容許任何人以任何違法方式挑戰法治。警方重申，任何人無合法辯解而摧毀或損壞屬於他人的財產，最高可判處監禁10年。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"紅官都叫攻擊？佢地係反共產黨架咩？"},{"pid":"3af1f670a36fd1e181794b6bf9dadd01a524cd41","tid":2068370,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84a125444dc3ff2a9ef42345031592e66bd6cc2d","tid":2068370,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddfe2d2125b82a245a840357d844fcebb411ef66","tid":2068370,"uid":10056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"奇撚怪..16號早上報警姐係15號梁義士果晚寫架啦 果晚明明條梯貼滿貼紙寫滿哂野 佢第2朝清哂其他 剩係留依句係到係有咩目的?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得係特登做文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea214976b3e85d607d956717ca9fac49f5d489","tid":2068370,"uid":54841,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"d6e3538c7b14c30fbbc391d8bca1d3d17b858f54","tid":2068370,"uid":251732,"like":42,"dislike":20,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"真正行出去冒險既人 <br />\n唔同我地班冷氣軍師割 <br />\n已經要十萬分致謝<br />\n<br />\n幾時輪到我地講割唔割"},{"pid":"5fc923cc1b70f57573b99e064607dbdc874d88be","tid":2068370,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a57df39a112428fbf2d3246509be53995a5b155","tid":2068370,"uid":307619,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:49:54.000Z","msg":"希望美國佬可以幾班紅官斬首"},{"pid":"580879fba8287d3bd502f152c222be9237ad2028","tid":2068370,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ec67f87e6dd07470e7a95683f29be05640fc40","tid":2068370,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"塗鴉會影響法治?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b0d87ccf4252366c6860f2a46598e788d754f3","tid":2068370,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"對字跡查下邊個暴徒所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c77141ef352ba2492ea76c096fa6045586803","tid":2068370,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"點算.....我覺得會拉倒人<br />\n唔係想嚇, 但黑警平時需要佢地果時從來都唔做野, 但要搵人佢地真係有心搵好可能會搵倒"},{"pid":"7c5358189aa1e0ee7bcf691732d32c5d70e86643","tid":2068370,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「嚴重損害法院的權威及打擊公眾對司法制度的信心」</span><br />\n<br />\n只有你自己先可以令到公眾冇哂信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040ee97e5a5d19401551af5cdfcc827b42412d50","tid":2068370,"uid":254505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim